## One user collection [/users/{username}]

### Show one user [GET]

+ Parameters
    + username (text) - username of a user

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 1,
            "firstname": "Test",
            "lastname": "Test",
            "username" : "test",
            "gender": 0,
            "password": "testtest"
        }

